@node "TARGET RENEGADE"
TARGET RENEGADE

On the high score table enter your name as "PA...." for infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "TEARAWAY THOMAS"
TEARAWAY THOMAS

You can stop the timer by typing "TIMEFLIESLIKEABANANA" at any time.

There is a secret level located on level 1.3 which can be found by climbing
up to the ninth branch of the tree (the one with the birds on it), and
running off the end.  You then will be whisked off to a room containing some
diamonds which can be collected for extra points.
@endnode
@node "TEENAGE MUTANT HERO TURTLES"
TEENAGE MUTANT HERO TURTLES

On the security code entry screen, enter the code "8859" and press 'RETURN'
then enter code "1506" and again press 'RETURN'.  Now enter the correct entry
code and then when playing the game pressing the 'HELP' key will give you
infinite energy.

When the code screen appears, enter the code as "1506".  It will say you are
wrong, so enter the code "8859", now enter the real code.  Now during the
game press the 'HELP' key to get infinite energy, and press 'HELP' again to
turn it off!
@endnode
@node "TERMINATOR II"
TERMINATOR II

To skip levels, pause the game and press every function key consecutively in
asending order.  Then unpause the game by pressing the fire button.  Then to
skip levels just press the 'escape' key.
@endnode
@node "TERMINATOR II-THE ARCADE VERSION"
TERMINATOR II-THE ARCADE VERSION

When the game has loaded select your control method at the options screen as
usual.  Instead of going to "Start Game", press 'ESC'.  Wait for the high
score chart with the picture of the "T-1000" to appear.  As soon as the last
digit is printed on the high score chart (the last 0 on the 10000, in 10th
place), click the left mouse button (or the joystick fire button if that's
plugged in to port one).  Note you must click the button 0.19 seconds after
the last digit on the high score chart has been printed on the screen.  If
you take longer, or click before the last digit is printed, the cheat will
not work, so, precise timing is required.  If you find this difficult there
is an alternative.  Hold down the fire button or left mouse button at the
high score table until it is finished.  Although this won't always work.  Go
back to the options screen.  If you can see the picture of Arnie, but no
options are displayed, then the cheat worked.  Left click on the mouse (or
joystick) to move on.  Click again to skip the high score display.  If you
allow the high score chart to be printed again the game may mess up.  Start
the game.

If you didn't get it to work restart the whole procedure.

Once you've started playing, you'll notice that a gunpowder and energy
readings are displayed for player two even though he isn't active.  Now pause
the game (press 'P' not 'F1') and type in all the function keys in
ascending numerical sequence and you should skip the level you are presently
playing.  This cheat is for one player only.
@endnode
@node "TEST DRIVE"
TEST DRIVE

Start the game and hold down the FIRE BUTTON, 'ALT', and 'C' for infinite
lives.  Hold down the fire button, 'ALT', and 'L' to access any level at any
time (only use one or the other).

Holding down the fire button on your joystick while going round a corner will
prevent you from sliding.

To get a highscore without playing the game, load the "highscores" file into
a text editor and edit it as desired (Note that the highscore shouldn't
exceed 99,999 and the name musn't be more than 15 characters). Then resave
it.

To change the car, load the "highscores" file as above, and use any of these
codes (They must be in lower case):

   p911t - Porsche 911 Turbo
   vette - Corvette
   lotus - Turbo Esprit
   rossa - Ferrari Testerossa
  counta - Lamborgini Countach
@endnode
@node "TEST DRIVE II"
TEST DRIVE II

Try typing the following during the game for interesting results:

   "GASS" - To jump to the Gas Station with an amazing time and score.
   "AERF" - For Faster acceleration and quicker braking, plus an extra life.
            Keep retyping it for lots of extra lives.
  "BRUCE" - Change the sign on level 2 to "Bruce Dawson wrote this",
  "GASST" - To jump to the Gas Station but use your real time and score.

On level 2 type "BRULE" to make road signs change.
@endnode
@node "THEATRE OF DEATH"
THEATRE OF DEATH

Enter "SHED SOFTWARE" as your password for infinite ammo.
@endnode        
