  10 - "0948 091 63 20"    13 - "0006 043 39 10"    19 - "0617 100 57 06"
@endnode
@node "THREE STOOGES"
THREE STOOGES

To really slow down the hang that selects the scenes, do the slapping game
and pull Curly's ear; do it continuously until time runs out.

When your on the "Doctor Wanted" stage of the game, drive your buggies at the
same speed as the male nurse pushing the patient, keeping a bit behind them.
This enables you to run up a high score without danger of collision.
@endnode
@node "THRUST"
THRUST
                    
From the desktop, insert the game disk.  Look for the "CHEAT.PRG" icon and
double-click on it.  You can survive collisions by typing cheat during the
game.
@endnode
@node "THUNDERBIRDS"
THUNDERBIRDS

Here are some passwords:

  Level 1 (Mine Menace)         --------
  Level 2 (Sub Crash):          RECOVERY
  Level 3 (The bank Job):       ALOYSIUS
  Level 4 (Countdown to Terror: ANDERSON
@endnode
@node "THUNDER BLADE"
THUNDER BLADE

To skip levels type in "CRASH" when the game has completely finished loading,
and the picture from the film "Blue Thunder' appears.  On pressing the 'H'
key, the screen should flash to signify that the cheat is active.  To access
the next level press 'HELP'.
@endnode
@node "THUNDER BURNER"
THUNDER BURNER

During play, press 'F10' and jiggle the joystick.  You'll now be able to
fast-forward or rewind.
@endnode
@node "THUNDER CATS"
THUNDER CATS

On the "Rescue Tygra" stage, find the place where bonus' pop up frequently,
and keep getting them.  If you are careful not to die, you can horde a lot
of free men.
@endnode
@node "THUNDERJAWS"
THUNDERJAWS

To skip levels, put the mouse into the Joystick Port and hold the left mouse
button down and press 'S'.  Now follow this by pressing the right mouse
button.
@endnode
@node "TIME MACHINE"
TIME MACHINE

A level cheat exists for this game.  Get a high score and enter the word
"DIZZY".  Now you can skip to any zone just by pressing the relevant number
keys.  Press 'A' or 'S' to jump sections of each time zone.
@endnode
