@node "TIMES OF LORE (Origin)"
TIMES OF LORE (Origin)

A brown scroll kills all monsters on the screen.
A white scroll freezes all monsters on the screen for a limited time (act
now!).
A green scroll teleports (can be used only twice).

A white potion randomly refuels energy.
A green potion completly refuels energy.

The Boots of speed are in Treela.
The magic axe is in Lankwell.

Save your game often!  When playing at night, turn up the contrast and
brightness settings (it won't make the game any smarter, though!).
@endnode
