@node "TITUS THE FOX"
TITUS THE FOX

During play hold down both 'AMIGA' keys, 'C' and press 'F4'.  You will be
presented with a message and will get 99 lives.

Level codes:

    1) ON THE FOXY TRAIL - 2625            9) HOME OF THE PHARAOHS - 1331
    2) LOOKING FOR CLUES - 8455           10) DESERT EXPERIENCE - 8612
    3) ROAD WORKS AHEAD - 2974            11) WALLS OF SAND - 4187
    4) GOING UNDERGROUND - 4916           12) A BEACON OF HOPE - 1350
    5) FLAMING CATACOMBS - 1933           13) A PIPE DREAM - 2290
    6) COMING TO TOWN - 0738              14) GOING HOME - 5052
    7) FOXY'S DEN - 2237                  15) JUST MARRIED - 2045
    8) ON THE ROAD TO MARRAKESH - 5648    16)              - 2578
@endnode    
@node "TOKI"
TOKI

If you type "KILLER" during the game, the screen will flash, activating the
in-game trainer and infiite lives.  You will now be able to start on any
level, by using the function keys 'F1' - 'F8'.

If you type 'KILLER' a second time, the screen will turn upside down!

This makes it quite hard to play.

During the intro, press 'ESC' then type "POORTOKI".  Start the game and press
'ESC' once the map screen has passed.  Then pressing function keys during the
intro will allow you to skip levels.
@endnode
@node "TOP SECRET (Amiga Power #17 Cover Disk)"
TOP SECRET (Amiga Power #17 Cover Disk)

Press 'F10' to skip levels

Type in "MOOG" on the high score table.  The screen will flash red and in the
next game there will be no collision detection.
@endnode
@node "TORVAK THE WARRIOR"
TORVAK THE WARRIOR

Type "CHEAT" on the high-score table followed by as many periods as you can
fit into the table.  Then during play, to skip levels, hold down the fire
button and press '1' - '5' to skip to the desired level.
@endnode
@node "TOTAL ECLIPSE"
TOTAL ECLIPSE

In-game hold down '1' and '9' (not on the numeric keypad) while pressing fire
to see the firework display.
@endnode
@node "TOWER OF BABEL"
TOWER OF BABEL

When collecting klondikes, turn the grabber to face them and program it with
fire, right, right, right, right and fire again.  The game thinks that you
have collected two klondikes so each level is only half as hard.
@endnode
@node "TOTAL RECALL"
TOTAL RECALL

On the title screen type "LISTEN TO THE WHALES" (with spaces) and the screen
should flip over,indicating that in-game you will have infinite energy.  Also
when you reach the taxi level either type "JIMMY HENDRIX" (with spaces) or
"JIMI HENDRIX" for an indestructable cab.

Solve for Level 1

First, go right, collect the gun, then run to the right and jump over the 
first lift.  Keep running to the next lift, go up three times and walk onto
the lift that is waiting when you arrive.  Go up, then left and collect the
gun.  Now go right to the next lift and down once.  Go onto the next lift,
and go up as far as you can see.  Walk right, off the lift and run right to
the next lift, picking up the object on the way.  Go up on the lift, run
right and go down three times on the next one that you come to.  Run left,
go down on the lift and run left again to collect the object.  Run right to
the first lift and go up, then go to the next lift and go up twice.  Run
right and go up on the lift once, then run and jump right.  Collect the
heart, run right,drop down through the hole and run to the exit.
@endnode
@node "TOWER OF BABEL"
TOWER OF BABEL

When collecting klondikes, turn the grabber to face them and program it with
fire, right, right, right, right and fire again.  The game thinks that you
have collected two klondikes so each level is only half as hard.
@endnode
@node "TOYOTA CELICA G.T. RALLY"
TOYOTA CELICA G.T. RALLY

In-game press the 'CONTROL' key and 'C' together to finish the race.

Another cheat says do the above at the start of a stage and you can finish
with a time of 00:00:00
@endnode
@node "TRAILBLAZER"
TRAILBLAZER

Hold down the 'Help', 'I', '1', and '2' keys and then type "CHEAT".  Now 'F3'
will remove gravity, 'F5' will change ball shape, 'F6' will change other 
player's balls.  'Help' will produce a laugh.
@endnode
@node "TRAINED ASSASSIN"
TRAINED ASSASSIN
Let the demo start, then press and hold down '2', '4', 'Y', the left
cursor key and '7' on the numeric keypad for infinite lives.  Also if you
hold down 'A', 'T', '.', '4', and 'ENTER' on the numeric keypad, 'F1' - 'F5'
will change the level.
@endnode
@node "TRANSARCTICA"
TRANSARCTICA

On the option screen, place the mouse pointer in a corner of the screen and
press the LEFT MOUSE BUTTON, 'CTRL' and 'ALT', all together to access the
cheat mode.

Click in the top left corner-For the supertrain (fully loaded)
Click in the top right corner-For the superenemy (super enemy)
Click in the bottom left corner-For Superscenario (everything)
Click in the bottom right corner-For victory
@endnode
@node "TRANSPLANT"
TRANSPLANT

Press 'F10' on the selection screen to activate the cheat mode.
@endnode
@node "TRANSWAR"
TRANSWAR

On the title screen, type "ALEXANDRA" for infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "TRANSWORLD"
TRANSWORLD

Load a saved game, you can now buy $9.999.999 for free.
@endnode
@node "TRAPS 'N' TREASURES"
TRAPS 'N' TREASURES
    
On the first title screen, the one before you are asked to insert disk "B",
type "SCAMAGIC".  The screen should flash.  During play press 'P' for one
extra life.
        
During play, type "PKLABAUTERMANNP".  The screen will flash to let you know
it worked.  This will give you one free life.  Type this whenever you want
another life.  You can only have a maximum of nine lives.
@endnode
@node "TREASURE ISLAND DIZZY"
TREASURE ISLAND DIZZY

You can fly by typing "ICANFLY" at the start of the game.  Keep pressing up
and you will be flying with the best of them.

Type "EGGSONLEGS" for immunity and "EGGONASPRING" for a high jumping ability.

Hold down 'S', 'P', 'A', 'C' keys, and the 'Space' bar.  Now press 'C' to
disappear (Space makes you reappear).  When you have disappeared, the 'M' key
moves the map around.

Here are some objects, and where to use them:

CHEST                     - Below the Cliff
SNORKEL                   - In the water
GRAVEDIGGER SPADE         - In the grave on Island 2
MAGIC STONE               - Totem Pole (Island 2)
DETONATOR AND DYNAMITE    - Mine (Island 1)
AXE & BIBLE               - Bridge (Island 1)
POGO STICK                - Pogo place on ship
GOLD COINS                - The Shop
FIRE PROOF SUIT           - Smuggler's Cave (Island 2)
BRANDY                    - Shop
GOLD EGG                  - Shop
BRASS KEY                 - Smuggler's Cave
CROWBAR                   - Rock in Water
@endnode
