@node "TROLLS"
TROLLS

Enter the "Sodapop" level, but before hitting fire, push up on the joystick
and hold down 'K' while pressing the fire button to begin the level.  Release
the key only when the level has started.  Now press 'Escape' to complete the 
level.
@endnode
@node "TUBULAR WORLDS"
TUBULAR WORLDS

On the title screen when the title appears or on the options screen, type:
"TODAZ IS HER BIRTHDAZ" if your using an American amiga or type:
"TODAY IS HER BIRTHDAY" if the 'Y' and 'Z' keys are switched (the 'Y' be next
to the 'X' key.  Now use the following keys during play:
 
 'E' -       Toggles infinite lives.
 'H' -       Gives you rockets.
 'I' -       Adds one to your shields.
 'L' -       Not sure.
 'N' -       Skip to next level.
 'R' -       Restart current level. 
 'S' -       Gives you an orb shield.
 '1' - '7' - Select various weapons.
 
When you go to press one of the keys let off on the fire button.
@endnode
@node "TURBO OUTRUN"
TURBO OUTRUN

After the countdown, type in "WEARPEEPEL".  Now to get more turbos, press
'D', press 'F' to see the ending, or 'G' to lose a credit.
@endnode
@node "TURN IT"
TURN IT
            Level 10 = APRIKOSE
            Level 20 = MANDEL
            Level 30 = KIRSCHE
            Level 40 = PFIRSISCH
@endnode            
@node "TURRICAN"
TURRICAN

To get 99 lives: Get a high score more than 20,000 and quit game.  It will go
to the high score table.  TYPE "BLUESMOBIL" and hit 'Return'.  On the next
play you will see 99 lives on the bottom of the screen, and have loads of
mines, lasers, etc.

This is more of a bug than a cheat, but here's a technique you can use in
Turrican:  If you come to a bad guy that you don't want to deal with, leave
the screen and then come back.  The bad guy should be gone.  Unfortunately
this also happens to extra men and weapons.
@endnode
@node "TURRICAN II"
TURRICAN II

On the title scrren, press the 'HELP' key which will bring up the music menu.
Select Option one, then select it again before pressing the numbers '4' and
'2'.  Now just press 'ESC' twice to enter the game, and you now have infinite
lives.
@endnode
@node "TURRICAN III"
TURRICAN III

During play type any of the following:

 "DESTRUCT"...........Infinite devastating gargantuan bombs.
 "ETERNITY".................................Infinite energy.
 "BEAMMEUP".....................................Skip levels.
 "ROLLING"..........................Infinite rolling energy.
@endnode



        
        
